  - `nn.Embedding`
- ğŸ” Recursively inject LoRA layers using `apply_lora()`
- â„ï¸ Automatically freeze original layer weights
- ğŸ’¾ Save/load only the LoRA-specific parameters
- ğŸ§ª Includes PyTest-based test suite

